  - 790
By: Sri Ramakrishna
---
A man can reach God if he follows one path rightly. Then he can learn
about all the other paths. It is like reaching the roof by some means
or other. Then one is able to climb down by the wooden or stone
stairs, by a bamboo pole, or even by a rope.
